2019-05-25  Andras Varga

	ide/scave: optimize large selections on Browse Data page

	It takes forever to call idList.add() for each ID (O(n^2) complexity), do
	not use it.

	Remove warning about selecting many result items.

2019-05-25  Andras Varga

	scave: IDList: implemented equals(), bulkAdd() etc.

2019-05-25  Andras Varga

	ide/scave: Data Export dialog title and description tweak

2019-05-24  Andras Varga

	ide/scave: performance: IDList is no longer an IStructuredSelection

	This prevents innocent callers from unsuspectingly invoking toArray() on
	it, which was a performance disaster if IDList contains many thousands of
	IDs.

2019-05-24  Andras Varga

	ide/scave: IDListSelection performance improvement

	"Select all" in the Browse Data page could take forever, due to internal
	IDList <--> Long[] conversions. Now that IDListSelection stores an IDList
	instead of Long[], most of the conversion overhead could be eliminated.

